event Approval(address indexed owner, address indexed spender, uint256 value)
event LogRebase(uint256 indexed epoch, uint256 rebase, uint256 index)
event LogSupply(uint256 indexed epoch, uint256 totalSupply)
event Transfer(address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256 value)
function allowance(address owner_, address spender) view returns (uint256)
function approve(address spender, uint256 value) returns (bool)
function changeDebt(uint256 amount, address debtor, bool add)
function decreaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 subtractedValue) returns (bool)
function increaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 addedValue) returns (bool)
function permit(address owner, address spender, uint256 value, uint256 deadline, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s)
function rebase(uint256 profit_, uint256 epoch_) returns (uint256)
function rebases(uint256) view returns (uint256 epoch, uint256 rebase, uint256 totalStakedBefore, uint256 totalStakedAfter, uint256 amountRebased, uint256 index, uint256 blockNumberOccured)
function transfer(address to, uint256 value) returns (bool)
function transferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 value) returns (bool)
